  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And a few [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] days later, when I got out from the [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] court, that I got out to put me back in possession of the-- every factory that introduced-- that was a new law that every factory what is engaging more than 40 people has to be nationalized.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I have been left with the paper, and the factory is there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And did you find out what happened to your father?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the first day that I came to Radom, when Radom was liberated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A few days after the li-- the Radom was liberated, I came to Radom.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The first thing what I was trying to do-- couldn't see any Jews-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to go to the cemetery, because my mother, my brother, was buried there, to make a visit to my mother, my brother.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SIGHS] The cemetery was about four, five kilometers from the town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was walking four kilometers, six kilometers, three kilometers, backwards and forwards.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I couldn't find the place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I know exactly where the cemetery was, because that was a big-- Jews were living about 500 years there in-- in Radom.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I couldn't find the place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And actually, the cemetery was with a fence, a colossal fence from red bricks, the whole cemetery was-- I couldn't find even not a brick there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went into one of the villages-- villages to find out, where is the Jewish cemetery [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A villager came out, and I asked him, listen, could you tell me where the Jewish cemetery is?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as I was turned a little bit, he-- he just sinked in the air.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I couldn't find him anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
